data.description: Fall in LOVE with this stunning home built by acclaimed First Texas Homes in NWISD! An entertainer's dream, show your treasured ones a great time inside and out. A must have in Texas, the backyard is an extension of your living space with sparkling SALTWATER POOL, covered patio, expansive stamped-concrete decking. You'll enjoy this space year-round with the gas-HEATED POOL! Right inside is your gourmet kitchen featuring a spacious quartz kitchen island, gas cooktop, double ovens and large, walk-in pantry. Your guests won't miss anything from the open concept living room, enjoying the ambience of music from built-in speakers and the view of your custom, spiral staircase and gorgeous floor-to-ceiling stone fireplace. Move the gathering upstairs to play games or settle in for a movie in your home theatre. Working from home is a breeze in your main-floor office adorned with french doors leading to the covered front porch. Elementary and Middle Schools are walking distance.
